Subject: USB Printing Support - Zebra Printers
Description: (Zebra) USB Printer is being blocked and is not being identified as Zebra printer unless USB printing support is allowed which is not desirable as a global setting to allow. Only after allowing USB Printing Support was the Zebra device type identified.
Next_Steps__c: Fix was verified by the customer. ADO # 342625. Awaiting new agent deployment.
Solution_Comment__c: Fixed in Windows agents 6.2.3.0037 and later.
